SRS - Street Racing Syndicate back when the street racing scene was the thing to do. N4S Underground and Juiced were also to other competitors to this. Of course I loved them all though N4S Underground got more popularity and Juiced getting a sequel. 
This gem was forgotten about but loved this game. Story was meh, gameplay is great! With these games my favorite thing to do was to customize my vehicles. I could spend hours making cars look good. If you got a PS2 and love to customize and have a thing for racing games. It's a must have in your collection. . .

caption.text:
🎮The Last of Us Part II se lanzará en dos discos porque "será enorme"🎮
—————————————————————————— The Last of Us Part II se lanza el 21 de febrero y su edición física contará con dos discos, según la descripción de Best Buy. No es el primer caso -lo mismo sucedió el año pasado con Red Dead Redemption 2-, pero sí poco habitual.

Una de las razones la comentó ayer Neil Druckmann durante la presentación de su nuevo tráiler. El codirector asegura que es el juego "más ambicioso y más largo" en los 35 años de historia del estudio. "Para contar este tipo de historia el juego necesitaba ser enorme", apunta, antes de decir que lo que hemos visto en el tráiler no es más que una "pizca de la superficie de lo que el juego guarda •••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••••

caption.text:
So I got an announcement for this plan I’ve had for October. The YouTube channel, Tats TopVideos, made a video about their top 85 freeware horror games, as seen in the screenshot posted here. So what I’ve decided to do is that everyday starting tomorrow is that I’ll be covering games 31-1 and giving my own opinions on them. Seeing as this is basically opinions on opinions, chances are you’ll disagree about some of these games being the best of the indie horror genre. Also I covered only about a 1/3rd of the games mentioned so feel free to check out the whole video via the link in my profile. It’s an experiment but I hope you guys will enjoy and you’ll see some good games and some mediocre games and possibly me throwing beef at people who don’t know I exist. Lastly there were several games that ranked above the 31 point that I felt deserved a higher ranking and on Halloween I’ll be doing mini-reviews of those games as sort of an honorable–should’ve been higher–mention.

caption.text: Apex Legends gameplay🚤

Hari ini Garena BR didistribusikan kode untuk menebus kulit elit lulus berikutnya. Mereka kode untuk memenangkan dua kulit utama lulus samurai setan .
.
Kode dibagikan kepada beberapa petugas pengaruh dari Garena dan anggota beberapa serikat terkenal.
.
Semua influencer yang memenangkan kode akan atau telah membuat menarik dari kode, beberapa masih melakukan, seperti @brunoplayhard berpengaruh playhard yang mengeluarkan tantangan pada instagram nya:
.
"Saya berbagi cerita ini dengan seorang teman dan mengirim saya langsung! Aku akan mengambil 10 sampai mengirim lulus kulit selama hari "
.
The Garena juga merilis kode untuk anggota serikat terkenal, seperti: 4K MUDAH, ALLAH, LOS BESAR dan keras.
.
Menantikan pada petugas instagram influencer dari Garena, mengapa beberapa bahkan akan merilis kode!
.
Beberapa orang mengeluh tentang hal itu, karena dalam pandangan orang-orang ini, Garena tidak harus memberikan kulit untuk orang-orang dan / atau serikat terkenal jika itu adalah untuk memberikan satu, harus memberikan kepada semua orang. Tapi apa tentang Anda, apa yang Anda pikirkan

Never feel alone or depressed I’m always up for a new friend!! 🙃

caption.text:
Donning the fallout shirt and playing some red dead! My life has been full of obstacles this week, both mental and physical. It is easy for me to feel alone, anxious, and depressed when life sways toward the negative. On days like today where I want to jump out of my own skin, I remind myself that everything is temporary. Life is never easy, even on the good days. Without contrast - the good and bad, the yin and yang - happiness would have no meaning. Embrace the cloudy days filled with bad news, loneliness, and poorly placed paper cuts; acknowledge this feeling and remember it. Life is dynamic. Cry through the bad, dance through the good, and laugh through it all💜
.
.
.
.
.

caption.text:
#RCNANintendoStacks Day 7 highlight! We’d first like to thank everyone for participating this week. We absolutely loved each and every contribution! The best part was seeing how people turned such a simple concept - a stack of games - and let the creativity flow into something great. Now for the finale, participants were allowed to come up with any combination of retro items for their stacks. This photo went above and beyond - various games from different consoles, different consoles, special edition Pikachu N64, manga, and anime on VHS! Well done!
